Data model used by a 2D LIDAR RPLidarA1.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Scan
    Scan is the object returned by any RPLidar provider.
    ScanDistance
    Scan distances store information about: - angle measured - distance from the object - quality of the measure - start flag

Package ev3dev.sensors.slamtec.model Description

Data model used by a 2D LIDAR RPLidarA1. This package design the set of classes which model the data information which the sensor provides.
